  <brief_title>Minimizing Ventricular Pacing</brief_title>
  <official_title>Minimizing Right Ventricular Pacing in Dual-chamber Pacemaker Patients With Sinus Node Disease and First Degree Atrioventricular Block.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
