  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  prolonged PQ interval &gt; 200 ms,

          -  percentage of right ventricular pacing with standard AV delay &gt; 90.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  second or third degree atrioventricular block,

          -  permanent atrial fibrillation.
      </textblock>
